{
  "video_id": "yyemG7V5ynQ",
  "title": "Alan Siegel: Let's simplify legal jargon!",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 15260.0,
      "end_time": 18259.0,
      "text": "So, basically we have public leaders,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 18260.0,
      "end_time": 21260.0,
      "text": "public officials who are out of control;"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21260.0,
      "end_time": 23260.0,
      "text": "they are writing bills that are unintelligible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23260.0,
      "end_time": 25260.0,
      "text": "and out of these bills are going to come"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25260.0,
      "end_time": 30260.0,
      "text": "maybe 40,000 pages of regulations, total complexity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 30260.0,
      "end_time": 33260.0,
      "text": "which has a dramatically negative impact on our life."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 33260.0,
      "end_time": 37260.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;re a veteran coming back from Iraq or Vietnam"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 37260.0,
      "end_time": 41260.0,
      "text": "you face a blizzard of paperwork to get your benefits;"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 41260.0,
      "end_time": 43260.0,
      "text": "if you&#39;re trying to get a small business loan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 43260.0,
      "end_time": 45260.0,
      "text": "you face a blizzard of paperwork."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 45260.0,
      "end_time": 47260.0,
      "text": "What are we going to do about it? I define simplicity"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 47260.0,
      "end_time": 50260.0,
      "text": "as a means to achieving clarity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 50260.0,
      "end_time": 52260.0,
      "text": "transparency and empathy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 52260.0,
      "end_time": 55260.0,
      "text": "building humanity into communications."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 55260.0,
      "end_time": 58260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve been simplifying things for 30 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 58260.0,
      "end_time": 61260.0,
      "text": "I come out of the advertising and design business."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 61260.0,
      "end_time": 65259.0,
      "text": "My focus is understanding you people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 65260.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67260.0,
      "text": "and how you interact with the government"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 67260.0,
      "end_time": 69260.0,
      "text": "to get your benefits,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 69260.0,
      "end_time": 72260.0,
      "text": "how you interact with corporations to decide whom you&#39;re going to do business with,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 72260.0,
      "end_time": 75260.0,
      "text": "and how you view brands."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 75260.0,
      "end_time": 79260.0,
      "text": "So, very quickly, when President Obama said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 79260.0,
      "end_time": 81260.0,
      "text": "\"I don&#39;t see why we can&#39;t"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 81260.0,
      "end_time": 85260.0,
      "text": "have a one-page, plain English consumer credit agreement.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 85260.0,
      "end_time": 87260.0,
      "text": "So, I locked myself in a room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 87260.0,
      "end_time": 90260.0,
      "text": "figured out the content,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 90260.0,
      "end_time": 93260.0,
      "text": "organized the document, and wrote it in plain English."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 93260.0,
      "end_time": 95260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve had this checked by the two top"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 95260.0,
      "end_time": 97260.0,
      "text": "consumer credit lawyers in the country."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 97260.0,
      "end_time": 99260.0,
      "text": "This is a real thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 99260.0,
      "end_time": 102260.0,
      "text": "Now, I went one step further and said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 102260.0,
      "end_time": 104260.0,
      "text": "\"Why do we have to stick with the stodgy lawyers"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 104260.0,
      "end_time": 108260.0,
      "text": "and just have a paper document? Let&#39;s go online.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 108260.0,
      "end_time": 110260.0,
      "text": "And many people"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 110260.0,
      "end_time": 112260.0,
      "text": "might need help in computation."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 112260.0,
      "end_time": 114260.0,
      "text": "Working with the Harvard Business School,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 114260.0,
      "end_time": 118260.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ll see this example when you talk about minimum payment:"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 118260.0,
      "end_time": 121260.0,
      "text": "If you spent 62 dollars for a meal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 121260.0,
      "end_time": 124260.0,
      "text": "the longer you take to pay out that loan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 124260.0,
      "end_time": 126260.0,
      "text": "you see, over a period of time using the minimum payment"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 126260.0,
      "end_time": 129259.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s 99 dollars and 17 cents."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 129258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 132260.0,
      "text": "How about that? Do you think your bank is going to show that to people?"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 132260.0,
      "end_time": 134260.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s going to work. It&#39;s more effective"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 134260.0,
      "end_time": 136260.0,
      "text": "than just computational aids."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 136260.0,
      "end_time": 138260.0,
      "text": "And what about terms like"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 138260.0,
      "end_time": 141260.0,
      "text": "\"over the limit\"?"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 141260.0,
      "end_time": 143260.0,
      "text": "Perhaps a stealth thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 143260.0,
      "end_time": 145260.0,
      "text": "Define it in context. Tell people what it means."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 145260.0,
      "end_time": 147260.0,
      "text": "When you put it in plain English,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 147260.0,
      "end_time": 149260.0,
      "text": "you almost force the institution"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 149260.0,
      "end_time": 151260.0,
      "text": "to give the people a way, a default out of that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 151260.0,
      "end_time": 153260.0,
      "text": "and not put themselves at risk."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 153260.0,
      "end_time": 156260.0,
      "text": "Plain English is about"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 156260.0,
      "end_time": 158260.0,
      "text": "changing the content."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 158260.0,
      "end_time": 160260.0,
      "text": "And one of the things I&#39;m most proud of"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 160260.0,
      "end_time": 162260.0,
      "text": "is this agreement for IBM."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 162260.0,
      "end_time": 164260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a grid, it&#39;s a calendar."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 164260.0,
      "end_time": 166260.0,
      "text": "At such and such a date, IBM has responsibilities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 166260.0,
      "end_time": 168260.0,
      "text": "you have responsibilities."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 168260.0,
      "end_time": 172260.0,
      "text": "Received very favorably by business."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 172260.0,
      "end_time": 174260.0,
      "text": "And there is some good news to report today."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 174260.0,
      "end_time": 176260.0,
      "text": "Each year, one in 10 taxpayers"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 176260.0,
      "end_time": 178260.0,
      "text": "receives a notice from the IRS."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 178260.0,
      "end_time": 181260.0,
      "text": "There are 200 million letters that go out."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 181260.0,
      "end_time": 184260.0,
      "text": "Running through this typical letter that they had,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 184260.0,
      "end_time": 186260.0,
      "text": "I ran it through my simplicity lab,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 186260.0,
      "end_time": 188260.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s pretty unintelligible."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 188260.0,
      "end_time": 192260.0,
      "text": "All the parts of the document in red are not intelligible."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 192260.0,
      "end_time": 194260.0,
      "text": "We looked at doing over 1,000 letters that cover"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 194260.0,
      "end_time": 197260.0,
      "text": "70 percent of their transactions in plain English."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 197260.0,
      "end_time": 199260.0,
      "text": "They have been tested in the laboratory."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 199260.0,
      "end_time": 201260.0,
      "text": "When I run it through my lab,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 201260.0,
      "end_time": 203260.0,
      "text": "this heat-mapping shows everything"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 203260.0,
      "end_time": 205260.0,
      "text": "is intelligible."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 205260.0,
      "end_time": 207260.0,
      "text": "And the IRS has introduced the program."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 207260.0,
      "end_time": 212260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 212260.0,
      "end_time": 215260.0,
      "text": "There are a couple of things going on right now"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 215260.0,
      "end_time": 217260.0,
      "text": "that I want to bring to your attention."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 217260.0,
      "end_time": 219260.0,
      "text": "There is a lot of discussion now"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 219260.0,
      "end_time": 221260.0,
      "text": "about a consumer financial protection agency,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 221260.0,
      "end_time": 223260.0,
      "text": "how to mandate simplicity."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 223260.0,
      "end_time": 225260.0,
      "text": "We see all this complexity."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 225260.0,
      "end_time": 227260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s incumbent upon us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 227260.0,
      "end_time": 229260.0,
      "text": "and this organization, I believe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 229260.0,
      "end_time": 232260.0,
      "text": "to make clarity, transparency"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 232260.0,
      "end_time": 235260.0,
      "text": "and empathy a national priority."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 235260.0,
      "end_time": 237260.0,
      "text": "There is no way that we should allow government"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 237260.0,
      "end_time": 239260.0,
      "text": "to communicate the way they communicate."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 239260.0,
      "end_time": 241260.0,
      "text": "There is no way we should do business"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 241260.0,
      "end_time": 244260.0,
      "text": "with companies that have agreements"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 244260.0,
      "end_time": 246260.0,
      "text": "with stealth provisions and that are unintelligible."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 246260.0,
      "end_time": 248260.0,
      "text": "So, how are we going to change the world?"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 248260.0,
      "end_time": 253260.0,
      "text": "Make clarity, transparency and simplicity a national priority."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 253260.0,
      "end_time": 255260.0,
      "text": "I thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 255260.0,
      "end_time": 260260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}